TALK Narrator You can change all of the controls in the game by pressing Escape and selecting Options in the menu
TALK Narrator Select Configure Controls using the arrow keys and press Return
TALK Narrator Use the arrow keys to select the control you want to change and press Return.
TALK Narrator Next, press the key that you want to use instead.
TALK Narrator Regardless of what keys you choose, you can always navigate the menus using the arrow keys and Return
TALK Narrator When you have finished configuring the keys, go right to the next Action Point
